      "content": "thanks for the warning. i'll definitely stay away from the wires. i was thinking maybe it's just a blown capacitor since i've heard that's a common thing? i've seen some videos online about how to swap them out but i'm not sure if i should try to at least test it with a multimeter or if that's too much. also is there anything else that would make that specific humming/vibrating sound without the motor actually kicking in?",
